      <h2>Generative Art Systems</h2>

      <p>Generative art uses autonomous systems to create artwork. The artist designs the rules and constraints, then lets the system explore the possibility space, often producing surprising and delightful results.</p>

      <div class="generative-showcase">
        <div class="generator-controls">
          <h3>Interactive Generator</h3>
          <div class="control-panel">
            <div class="control-group">
              <label for="complexity">Complexity</label>
